  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment: 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2). Intended use: pre-market submission support for Class II CPB device hemolysis QoI under steady-state adult CPB flow conditions (3–6 L/min, 60–120 mmHg). NOTE — structured hasContextOfUse link is intentionally absent per ProfileMinimal declaration; use-scope is conveyed only through Claim and Requirement prose.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cpb-hemolysis-mrl2",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cpb-hemolysis-cfd-adequate",
