    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. The CFD hemolysis model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device in support of 510(k) submission. The intended use scope — adult CPB hemolysis prediction under steady-state conditions at the specified operating envelope — is fully described in the Claim (https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cpb-hemolysis-cfd-adequate) and Requirement (https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cpb-hemolysis-mrl2) documents referenced by this UoA.",
